 2. Declare a global variable of the `interface`&#39;s type.
 3. Initialize the variable in the `onAttach` method of the fragment.
 4. Nullify the variable in the `onDestroy` method.
 5. Call the interface methods in the buttons you want.
 6. Implement the `interface` in the `activity` and handle the callback methods.

